               <note>
                  <date type="foundation" notBefore="1300" notAfter="1400">1300-1400</date>
                  <desc type="foundation">The foundation date mentioned by the local oral tradition is <date>1295 year of mercy</date>, but it is linked to
                  the time of <persName ref="PRS3429DawitII">ʾaṣe Dāwit</persName>.
                  According to the same tradition, the
                     founder was ʾabuna <persName ref="PRS6620Mamas">Māmās</persName> (from the time of King <persName ref="PRS8595SayfaAr">Sayfa ʾArʿad</persName>, r.
                     <date>1344-1371</date> and his successor <persName ref="PRS3429DawitII"/>).</desc>
                  <ab type="history">Gatar, formerly gadām. According to the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1428GadlaB">Vita of saint Ba-ṣalota
                     Mikāʾel of Dabra Gol</ref> (ʾAmhārā), Ba-ṣalota Mikāʾel was exiled to <placeName ref="LOC3640GuloMa">Gulo Makadā</placeName> and died at Gʷǝdgʷǝde,
                     which seems to have been a name of the area around ʾAgarhǝse.
                     Local tradition remembers him and confirms that his
                     burial place is in the vicinity.
                   </ab>
                  <ab type="description">
                     <figure>
                        <graphic url="Sites/AQM.tif">
                           <desc>The church photographed by Denis Nosnitsin during the Ethio-SPaRe project.</desc>
                        </graphic>
                     </figure>
                     25 Mss.; 10 Mss. photographed: <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm001">AQM-001</ref> "Vita of Mamas"; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm002">AQM-002</ref> "Vita of Mamas"; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm003">AQM-003</ref> "Four Gospels"; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm004">AQM-004</ref> "The Book of the Baptismal Rite"; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm005">AQM-005</ref> "Miracles of Jesus"; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm006">AQM-006</ref> "Miracles of Mary"; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm007">AQM-007</ref> "Miracles of Jesus"; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm008">AQM-008</ref> "Missal"; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm009">AQM-009</ref> "Missal"; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESaqm010">AQM-010</ref> "The Book of the Funeral Rite"
                   </ab>

                  <ab type="tabot">
                     <measure quantity="4"/>Tābots of <persName ref="PRS6819Mary" type="tabot">Mary</persName>,
                     <persName ref="PRS7049Michael" type="tabot">Michael</persName>, <persName ref="PRS13452Mamas" type="tabot">Māmās</persName>, <persName ref="PRS8083Raphael" type="tabot">Raphael</persName>
                     The main feast is that of <persName ref="PRS13452Mamas">Māmās</persName> on <date>30 Tāḫśāś</date>.</ab>
